des: Juniper Certify contains a set of multiple-choice practice questions applicable to Associate-level exams, including the JNCIA-Junos, JNCIA-DevOps, JNCIA-SEC, JNCIA-DC, JNCIA-MistAI, JNCIA-Design, and JNCIA-Cloud. You can choose questions based on your area of focus. Responses include explanations of concepts included in the exam objectives.
